  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 1</strong> Enchantment</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nOne creature of your choice that you can see within range hears a discordant melody in its mind. The target makes a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, it takes 3d6 Psychic damage and must immediately use its Reaction|XPHB, if available, to move as far away from you as it can, using the safest route. On a successful save, the target takes half as much damage only.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 3d6|1-9|1d6 for each spell slot level above 1.</p>",
